Simon Cadell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_Cadell 0 Simon John Cadell (19 July 1950 – 6 March 1996) was an English actor, best known for his portrayal of Jeffrey Fairbrother in the first five series of the BBC situation comedy Hi-de-Hi!.
